    %p
      %span.weinre weinre
      is a debugger for web pages, like
      FireBug (for FireFox)
      and
      Web Inspector (for WebKit-based browsers), except it's designed
      to work
      = succeed "," do
        %b remotely
      = succeed "." do
        %b
          allow you debug web pages
          on a mobile device such as a phone
